---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Onchain AMM — Permissionless Markets">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Permissionless Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">無需許可的市場</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Onchain AMM</span><span class="lang-zh">鏈上自動化做市商</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">Permissionless financial markets where anyone can list, trade, or provide liquidity — no exchange approval, no designated market maker, no trading hours.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">無需許可嘅金融市場 — 任何人都可以上市、交易或提供流動性，唔使交易所審批、唔使指定做市商、唔使交易時段。</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Stats grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$1-2B</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Uniswap daily vol</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap日交易量</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">24/7</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Markets open</span><span class="lang-zh">市場全天候</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">x·y=k</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Pricing formula</span><span class="lang-zh">定價公式</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1000s</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">New tokens daily</span><span class="lang-zh">每日新代幣</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">In traditional markets, listing a new security requires exchange approval, regulatory filing, and a designated market maker agreement. Onchain, you create a liquidity pool and the market exists. No application, no approval, no trading hours. Uniswap, the largest decentralized exchange on Ethereum, processes $1 to $2 billion in daily volume. Raydium and Meteora handle comparable volume on Solana. Thousands of new tokens are listed every day — permissionless financial markets, operating 24/7.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">在傳統市場，上市一隻新證券需要交易所審批、監管備案同指定做市商協議。在鏈上，你建立一個liquidity pool，市場就存在。無需申請，無需審批，無交易時段。Uniswap，Ethereum上最大嘅去中心化交易所，日交易量$10至$20億。Raydium同Meteora在Solana上處理相當嘅交易量。每日有數千隻新代幣上市 — 無需許可嘅金融市場，24/7運作。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">How It Works: The Constant Product Formula</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">運作原理：恆定乘積公式</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">An automated market maker replaces the traditional orderbook with a mathematical formula. A pool contains two tokens — say ETH and USDC — and their quantities maintain a constant product: <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x × y = k</span>. When you buy Token A, the pool's supply of Token A decreases while Token B increases, and Token A's price rises automatically. No orderbook, no market maker placing orders — a smart contract quotes prices based on supply and demand.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">AMM用數學公式取代傳統orderbook。一個池入面有兩隻代幣 — 例如ETH同USDC — 佢哋嘅數量維持恆定乘積：<span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x × y = k</span>。你買Token A，池入面Token A供應就減少、Token B增加，Token A嘅price自動升。唔使orderbook，唔使做市商掛單 — smart contract根據供需自動報價。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Aggregators like Jupiter (Solana) and 1inch (Ethereum) automatically route trades across dozens of pools to find the best price. Settlement is instant — seconds, not T+1 or T+2. Assets stay in your wallet throughout. Non-custodial, no exchange intermediary.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">聚合器好似Jupiter（Solana）同1inch（Ethereum）會自動幫你搵幾十個池入面最好嘅price。結算即時 — 秒級，唔係T+1或T+2。資產全程留喺你錢包。Non-custodial，唔經交易所。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Three Things You Can Do</span><span class="lang-zh">三件你可以做嘅嘢</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">1. Trade — onchain swap.</span> Any token pair can be swapped as long as someone has created a pool. No listing requirement. This is the basic use case: buy and sell tokens with instant settlement and self-custody.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">1. 交易 — 鏈上swap。</span>只要有人建立咗池，任何代幣對都可以swap。唔使上市審批。呢個係最基本嘅用法：即時結算、自己hold住個錢包嚟買賣代幣。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">2. Provide liquidity — be the market maker.</span> Deposit two tokens into a pool and earn trading fees from every swap. In finance terms, this is going long two assets and short volatility. The P&L of the short vol position is called impermanent loss: when one token's price moves significantly relative to the other, your position is worth less than simply holding both tokens. Stablecoin pairs (USDC/USDT) offer low fees of 0.01 to 0.05% per swap with minimal impermanent loss — comparable to money market yields. New token launches can carry fee rates of 50 to 99%, generating significant short-term returns, but the underlying tokens are extremely volatile and frequently go to zero.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">2. 提供流動性 — 做做市商。</span>將兩隻代幣存入池中，從每筆交易賺取費用。用金融語言講，呢個係做多兩種資產加做空波動率。做空波動率倉位嘅盈虧叫做無常損失：當一隻代幣嘅價格相對另一隻大幅變動，你嘅倉位價值低過單純持有兩隻代幣。穩定幣對（USDC/USDT）每筆交易提供0.01至0.05%嘅低費率，無常損失最小 — 與貨幣市場收益相當。新代幣發行可有50至99%嘅費率，產生可觀嘅短期回報，但底層代幣波動極大且經常歸零。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">3. Launch a token — permissionless IPO.</span> Platforms like PumpFun and Raydium LaunchLab allow anyone to launch a token in seconds. Bonding curve pricing means early buyers get lower prices, and more buyers push the price up. At a certain market cap, the token automatically migrates to an AMM pool and becomes a fully tradeable market. Essentially a permissionless IPO — no underwriter, no prospectus, no lock-up period. Thousands launch daily. 99% are junk, but the infrastructure itself is a fundamental financial primitive: permissionless capital formation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">3. 發行代幣 — 無需許可嘅IPO。</span>PumpFun同Raydium LaunchLab等平台俾任何人幾秒之內launch一隻代幣。Bonding curve定價：早期買家price低，越多人買price越高。到一定market cap，代幣自動migrate去AMM池變成fully tradeable嘅market。本質上就係permissionless IPO — 冇underwriter、冇招股書、冇鎖定期。每日launch幾千隻。99%係垃圾，但呢個基礎設施本身係一個基本金融原語：唔使批准嘅資本形成。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">TradFi Comparison</span><span class="lang-zh">同傳統金融比較</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Where traditional markets require exchange approval and regulatory filing to list, onchain you just create a pool. Where traditional market making requires a designated MM agreement, onchain anyone can deposit liquidity. Trading hours go from 9:30am–4:00pm plus holidays to 24/7/365. Settlement goes from T+1 or T+2 to instant (seconds). Custody goes from broker/custodian to self-custody in your own wallet. Every structural friction in traditional markets — listing delays, settlement windows, custody transfers, trading hour limitations — is eliminated.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">傳統市場要交易所審批同監管備案先可以上市，鏈上只需建一個池。傳統做市要指定做市商協議，鏈上任何人都可以存入流動性。交易時間從9:30am–4:00pm加假期變成24/7/365。結算從T+1或T+2變成即時（秒級）。託管從經紀商揸住變成你自己錢包嘅self-custody。傳統市場每一個結構性摩擦 — 上市延遲、結算窗口、託管轉移、交易時段限制 — 全部冇咗。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Risks</span><span class="lang-zh">風險</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Impermanent loss is the fundamental cost of providing liquidity — price divergence between pooled tokens causes loss relative to simply holding. Smart contract bugs can lead to fund loss; only use audited protocols. Permissionless listing means anyone can create a token, and 99% of new tokens are worthless — rug pulls are common. None of this is regulated by the SFC, and there is no investor protection.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">無常損失係做LP嘅基本成本 — 池入面代幣price偏離就會令你蝕過淨hold。智能合約有bug可以令你蝕晒；只用經審計嘅協議。無需許可上市意味著任何人都可以建代幣，99%新代幣毫無價值 — rug pull成日發生。呢啲全部唔受SFC監管，冇投資者保障。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Getting Started</span><span class="lang-zh">如何開始</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Get a wallet — Phantom for Solana or MetaMask for Ethereum. Fund it with SOL or ETH from a licensed VATP like HashKey or OSL. Use an aggregator — Jupiter on Solana, 1inch on Ethereum — for the best prices across all pools. Start with stablecoin pairs if you want to try LP with lower risk.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">攞個錢包 — Solana用Phantom，Ethereum用MetaMask。從持牌VATP好似HashKey或OSL買SOL或ETH。用聚合器 — Solana用Jupiter，Ethereum用1inch — 跨所有池幫你搵最好price。如果想低風險試吓LP，從穩定幣對開始。</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-cyan-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Explore other onchain products</span><span class="lang-zh">了解其他鏈上產品</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Polymarket for prediction markets. Hyperliquid for perps + pre-IPO.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Polymarket做prediction markets，Hyperliquid做perps + pre-IPO。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href={`${base}/products/polymarket`} class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-cyan-500 text-black text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Polymarket</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-lg hover:border-zinc-500 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Hyperliquid</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
